Package: shinytemplate
Type: Package
Title: Template for developing shiny app as a package with live reloading
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Colin", "Diesh", email = "dieshcol@msu.edu", role = c("cre", "aut")))
Maintainer: Colin Diesh <dieshcol@msu.edu>
Description: shinytemplate allows you to develop a shiny app as a package that can be \
    live reloaded. This can be extended to create your own shiny apps as packages.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
Imports:
    tools (>= 3.2.3),
    shiny (>= 0.14.2),
Suggests:
    testthat
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
